Prerequisites
=============
Ruby 1.8.0 or later.

This code is supported on Windows NT, Windows 2000 or Windows XP Pro only.  It
may work on Windows XP Home, but it is not officially supported for that
platform.

To run the test suite, you will need the sys-proctable package, found at
http://ruby-sysutils.sf.net.

Installation Instructions
=========================
ruby extconf.rb
nmake
ruby test.rb        # optional
nmake site-install

How does fork on Win32 work exactly?
====================================
See the "Details" section of the documentation for how this bit of magic was
accomplished.

Sample code
===========
You can find examples for fork() and create() under doc/examples.